LED-System
http://website.tld

Description:
------------

Requirements:
-------------
* Arduino 0023
* Menu Library 1.0 (http://arduino.cc/playground/Code/Menu)
  * In the library folder, open the file "interfaces\SubMenuInterface.h" and
    change "MAXIMUM_SUBMENU_ITEMS" to 7 instead of 4. Otherwise the submenu
    cannot display all the items we require it to display for this project.
* Custom I2c/SPI LiquidCrystal Library (https://github.com/adafruit/LiquidCrystal)
* LPD6803 RGB Pixel Library (https://github.com/adafruit/LPD6803-RGB-Pixels)
* TimerOne Library (http://code.google.com/p/arduino-timerone/)

Acknowledgements:
-----------------
* Nunchuck code based on code from Grant Emsley (http://arduino.emsley.ca)
* Menu Library by Alexander Brevig

